      • setVisible

        void setVisible​(boolean visible)
        Sets the visibility of the layer. Any registered ILayer.OnLayerVisibleChangedListener instances should be notified if the visibility of the layer changes as a result of the invocation of this method.
        Parameters:
        visible - true to make the layer visible, false to make it invisible.
